IAlternation - Interface in grammars.seekWhence.disjunctions
IAlternation is an interface used for the expression of a disjunctive rule in the context-free grammar associated with the microworld 'SeekWhence'.
IChains - Interface in grammarModel.genericTools
IChains contains an indexed list of indexed lists of Strings, with navigation functionalities (a 'chain' is a list of Strings, so IChains is a list of chains).
IGenericFileReader - Interface in grammarModel.genericTools
IGenericFileReader allows the generation of a 'syntax grove' out of a text file, provided it contains lists of paths of syntax trees generated using a context-free grammar.

ISyntacticChains - Interface in grammarModel.genericTools
A ISyntacticChains is a list (endowed with navigation functionalities) of all the paths of a syntactic structure from its generated node to one of its terminals.
ISyntacticGrove - Interface in grammarModel.structure
ISyntacticGrove is a container of syntax trees, i.e. syntax branches whose name is the start element of the context-free grammar at use.
